{"tid":602349,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"【基督教】一個基督教，各自表述","createTime":"2018-03-23T03:10:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T16:24:22.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"aa4e2ae57ad643048908bbd6b9269e667659d685","tid":602349,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T03:10:14.000Z","msg":"天主教、東正教、基督教、基督新教各派、摩門教、耶證都屬同一個宗教，都就係基督教。<br />\n<br />\n只不過係，一個基督教，各自表述。<br />\n一本聖經，各自表述。<br />\n<br />\n教派不同的釋經，釋經方法。就如人大釋法一樣，釋到連教義都好似改變埋。釋經可以釋到變一教兩制。不過，點釋到好，其實大家都係耶撚。<br />\n<br />\n所以，耶教就係耶教，大家都係耶撚、耶人、耶青，無謂再分啦。"},{"pid":"1d5b215a6e646c03e411e15ffd78469e84dfd511","tid":602349,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T16:23:17.000Z","msg":"點睇馬太福音5:17?"},{"pid":"78af3fe4b2a72737b6cfd4b9a0e79cfe55fa6dc0","tid":602349,"uid":138142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T21:50:23.000Z","msg":"好似話猶太教都係來自聖經"},{"pid":"28c2e712bf6c659417afb396c3e29e4ae8406ef2","tid":602349,"uid":129931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T22:01:42.000Z","msg":"點睇偽經"},{"pid":"915c081a0d45c88c8fc5654f74e3925d22747e5f","tid":602349,"uid":79373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:29:17.000Z","msg":"耶証好L痴線 斷哂六親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連普通耶撚都嫌棄"},{"pid":"867412f4d2509d02524913c5403b89f21e824288","tid":602349,"uid":145230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:01:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b47632da2bb4fa507c93efe82158b4e25c753b10","tid":602349,"uid":145230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:24:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}